# gpt-5.4 second-attacker package (#9a): harness + baseline + gpt-5.4 answers + answer keys + scored summary.
# EXCLUDE the bulky batch_*.json prompt blobs (23M, dataset-derived, regenerable via scripts/cr_2afc_export.py).
!/gpt54_2afc_pkg/
/gpt54_2afc_pkg/tasks/*/batch_*.json

# gpt-5.4 second attacker on the FIXED cards (A2, cited certification): same layout + exclusions.
!/gpt54_2afc_fixed_pkg/
/gpt54_2afc_fixed_pkg/tasks/*/batch_*.json

# ============================================================================
# HARD DENY — must stay LAST so no whitelist rule above can re-include these.
# Per-line sanitize audit sidecars map card lines back to member text; they share
# the access level of raw member data and are NEVER shipped, in any directory.
# ============================================================================
*_audit.json
